{"tid":1790011,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"俄聯邦安全局發生槍擊 3人死亡包括警員","createTime":"2019-12-19T16:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T16:30:32.000Z","uid":222970,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ad8d280425c52afde5d120740686d276af236d0c","tid":1790011,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:25:18.000Z","msg":"俄聯邦安全局發生槍擊 3人死亡包括警員<br />\n<br />\n位於莫斯科市中心的俄羅斯聯邦安全局(FSB)大樓發生槍擊事件，有3人死亡，包括一名警員。<br />\n<br />\nFSB是俄羅斯的情報機關，前身是蘇聯國家安全委員會(KGB)，槍擊事件是在總部大樓的接待處發生。不過，俄羅斯《消息報》表示槍擊是在FSB總部附近發生。<br />\n<br />\n警方已封鎖現場，傳媒見到有配備自動武器的軍警戒備，至少有5架救護車駛離現場。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/英國天空新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191220/60397448\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191220%2F60397448&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5UBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=9cc55b9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191220%2F60397448&h=a669b755\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191220/60397448</a>"},{"pid":"511d5e256e3ac65c3ef61ffb929e1b6662f936c8","tid":1790011,"uid":126797,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:26:32.000Z","msg":"唔知點解一見到標題有警員死左，就有d開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過原來係俄羅斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />RIP..."},{"pid":"a7e0126df3278a1241857e04a9be905c163c3b24","tid":1790011,"uid":79562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"511d5e256e3ac65c3ef61ffb929e1b6662f936c8","tid":1790011,"uid":126797,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:26:32.000Z","msg":"唔知點解一見到標題有警員死左，就有d開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過原來係俄羅斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />RIP..."},"cit